\pard\f0\fs28 Umbel of 1-5(-7) flowers; spathe 1- or 2-valved. Flowers white or pale pink, campanulate, nodding. Hypanthial tube and corona absent. Perianth-segments all more or less alike. Filaments usually much shorter than anthers; anthers not apiculate. Capsule pyriform to subglobose, erect; pericarp somewhat fleshy; seeds numerous.
\par

